Package com.worldpay.sdk.wpg.request.hosted

Class HostedPaymentPagesRequest

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.worldpay.sdk.wpg.internal.xml.XmlRequest<RedirectUrl>
      • com.worldpay.sdk.wpg.request.hosted.HostedPaymentPagesRequest

  • public class HostedPaymentPagesRequest
extends com.worldpay.sdk.wpg.internal.xml.XmlRequest<RedirectUrl>
    Generates an order for taking payments using the Hosted Payment Pages (HPP) platform. This request will return a URL, which can be used to redirect the shopper or with the JavaScript SDK (for embedded payments).
    See Also:
    http://support.worldpay.com/support/kb/gg/corporate-gateway-guide/content/hostedintegration/quickstart.htm
